{"TopicId":154728,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"How do Kerbals fir their eyes through their helmets?","CreatedByName":"Souper","CreatedById":86003,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T12:49:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Souper","CreatedById":86003,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T12:49:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo they kinda wiggle them through or retract them into their heads?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Raging Sandwich","CreatedById":164377,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T12:51:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Image result for all seeing eye\u0022 src=\u0022http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/deusex/images/8/8e/All_seeing_eye.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20121208115833\u0026amp;path-prefix=en\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steuben","CreatedById":77368,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T14:10:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a theory which states that if ever anyone discovers exactly how they can do it,\u00A0they\u00A0will instantly\u00A0stop doing it that way\u00A0and do it using a method even more bizarre and inexplicable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is another theory mentioned, which states that this has already happened.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TopHeavy11","CreatedById":154744,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T14:32:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTheir born with them on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Finnan","CreatedById":130706,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T19:50:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey use grease.\u00A0 Lots and lots of grease.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flamingo","CreatedById":164519,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T19:57:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey use WD-40 of course. Just a little spray on each eye and they are ready to go!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dangerhamster","CreatedById":146944,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T20:10:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are some things mortal man is not meant to know. Along with where do all the biro\u0027s go, what exactly is inside Nigel Farage\u0027s head and how exactly does one perambulate this is one of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T20:42:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can answer that using the following image:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022oPyO3CJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/oPyO3CJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen a kerbal put his suit on he actually climbs in through the faceplate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen a Kerbal removes his helmet he as to climb out then get dressed again minus the helmet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-09T22:06:57Z\u0022 title=\u002201/09/2017 10:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Martian Emigrant\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-09T22:09:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd then being extra careful with their one larger bulging eye.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eddiew","CreatedById":127483,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T00:02:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInflatable helmets. Just soft plastic \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"septemberWaves","CreatedById":160814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T17:06:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClearly the helmets work Iron Man style, and assemble themselves around the kerbal\u0027s head from where they were stored in an illogically small compartment at the back of the suit. This also explains why the suits have the ability to fly - the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E is being primarily supplied by Kerbal Tony Stark*.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Actually, this explains just about everything about the space program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Carl","CreatedById":2645,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T20:02:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know, that does actually make sense...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcept for the lack of PA system for him to hijak...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-10T20:02:33Z\u0022 title=\u002201/10/2017 08:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Carl\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T20:13:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222916009\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221483992649\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146944\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dangerhamster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/9/2017 at 8:10 PM, dangerhamster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are some things mortal man is not meant to know. Along with where do all the biro\u0027s go, what exactly is inside Nigel Farage\u0027s head and how exactly does one perambulate this is one of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think the answer to your first question is suspiciously similar to the answer to your second question...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MinimalMinmus","CreatedById":172387,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T20:17:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne word, or rather, one trope.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YouDoNOTWantToKnow\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EYou do NOT want to know.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zhetaan","CreatedById":125721,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T20:24:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do\u00A0Kerbals fir their eyes through their helmets?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have one possible solution:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022h35hQRI.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/h35hQRI.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-10T20:29:08Z\u0022 title=\u002201/10/2017 08:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Zhetaan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JonathanPerregaux","CreatedById":152561,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T22:34:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would defer to an expert for his opinion on how this is accomplis\u2014\u003Cstrong\u003EOH MY GOD!!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022hqdefault.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jZYevkvj2s0/hqdefault.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qeveren","CreatedById":10381,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T22:41:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals obviously are akin to frogs:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/TUbx1tBnpG0?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacetraindriver","CreatedById":149403,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-10T23:50:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m pretty sure they could just tilt their head up?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"memes in space","CreatedById":171597,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-11T01:12:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222916009\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221483992649\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146944\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dangerhamster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/9/2017 at 3:10 PM, dangerhamster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhat exactly is inside Nigel Farage\u0027s head\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo much for no politics, huh?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso birds fly south when it\u0027s cold, answered your first question. Typos are bad, lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-11T02:12:33Z\u0022 title=\u002201/11/2017 02:12  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by memes in space\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u